{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0MzgwNjA0ODc0", "number": 2537, "title": "Fix a bug where `ctx.set*Timeout()` does not schedule a timeout", "bodyText": "... when no timeout was scheduled before.\nMotivation:\nWhen a timeout is not scheduled for a request, a new timeout set by\nset{Request,Response}Timeout does not work well.\nSee #2535\nModifications:\n\nMake set{Request,Response}Timeout call set{Request,Reponse}TimeoutAfterMillis\nif a timeout is not scheduled yet.\n\nResult:\nThe set{Request,Response}Timeout* properly set the new timeout when no timeout is scheduled.", "createdAt": "2020-02-27T02:32:34Z", "url": "https://github.com/line/armeria/pull/2537", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "95217b3b61d92bec6ced49286fd8a7d88e5dc259"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-02-28T04:52:34Z", "author": {"login": "ikhoon"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 6, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABcIR6iWAH2gAyMzgwNjA0ODc0OmQ1MTMyYWEzMDE3YzE0ZDUwYzhjYmIyMmJkNTYwMTg5MzJmOGQwOWY=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABcIlhBdAFqTM2NjEwODUzMw==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "d5132aa3017c14d50c8cbb22bd56018932f8d09f", "author": {"user": {"login": "ikhoon", "name": "Ikhun Um"}}, "url": "https://github.com/line/armeria/commit/d5132aa3017c14d50c8cbb22bd56018932f8d09f", "committedDate": "2020-02-27T02:29:48Z", "message": "Fix a bug where a timeout is not updated by `set{Request,Response}Timeout*`\n\nMotivation:\n\nWhen a timeout is not scheduled for a request, a new timeout set by\n`set{Request,Response}Timeout` does not work well.\nSee #2535\n\nModifications:\n\n- Make `set{Request,Response}Timeout` call `set{Request,Reponse}TimeoutAfterMillis`\n  if a timeout is not scheduled yet.\n\nResult:\nThe `set{Request,Response}Timeout*` properly set the new timeout when no timeout is scheduled."}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3MzY1NDQ2Mzky", "url": "https://github.com/line/armeria/pull/2537#pullrequestreview-365446392", "createdAt": "2020-02-27T06:49:54Z", "commit": {"oid": "d5132aa3017c14d50c8cbb22bd56018932f8d09f"}, "state": "COMMENTED", "comments": {"totalCount": 2, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpK0MjAyMC0wMi0yN1QwNjo0OTo1NFrOFvG4NA==", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpK0MjAyMC0wMi0yN1QwNjo1MDowN1rOFvG4cA==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDM4NDk0MDA4NA==", "bodyText": "responseTimeoutMillis > 0 is always true at this point.", "url": "https://github.com/line/armeria/pull/2537#discussion_r384940084", "createdAt": "2020-02-27T06:49:54Z", "author": {"login": "trustin"}, "path": "core/src/main/java/com/linecorp/armeria/client/DefaultClientRequestContext.java", "diffHunk": "@@ -459,6 +459,11 @@ public void setResponseTimeoutMillis(long responseTimeoutMillis) {\n             clearResponseTimeout();\n         }\n \n+        if (this.responseTimeoutMillis == 0 && responseTimeoutMillis > 0) {", "state": "SUBMITTED", "replyTo": null, "originalCommit": {"oid": "d5132aa3017c14d50c8cbb22bd56018932f8d09f"}, "originalPosition": 4}, {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDM4NDk0MDE0NA==", "bodyText": "Ditto", "url": "https://github.com/line/armeria/pull/2537#discussion_r384940144", "createdAt": "2020-02-27T06:50:07Z", "author": {"login": "trustin"}, "path": "core/src/main/java/com/linecorp/armeria/server/DefaultServiceRequestContext.java", "diffHunk": "@@ -339,6 +339,11 @@ public void setRequestTimeoutMillis(long requestTimeoutMillis) {\n             clearRequestTimeout();\n         }\n \n+        if (this.requestTimeoutMillis == 0 && requestTimeoutMillis > 0) {", "state": "SUBMITTED", "replyTo": null, "originalCommit": {"oid": "d5132aa3017c14d50c8cbb22bd56018932f8d09f"}, "originalPosition": 4}]}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "172aacc90e8154577696d493d2cd013985be2270", "author": {"us